    <h2>Refund eligibility</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        If you are unable to access the product due to a verified technical issue on our side, we will attempt to fix it.
        If we cannot resolve access within a reasonable timeframe, we will provide a refund.
      </li>
      <li>
        Refund requests must be submitted within 7 days of purchase.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Non-refundable situations</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Change of mind after access/delivery has been provided</li>
      <li>Incompatibility with your Notion plan, device, or third-party platform changes</li>
      <li>Failure to use the product as intended</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How to request a refund</h2>
    <p>
      Submit your request through the <a href="contact.html">Contact</a> page with:
      (1) purchase email, (2) purchase date, (3) reason for request, and (4) any relevant screenshots if access is failing.
    </p>

    <h2>Chargebacks</h2>
    <p>
      If you have an issue, contact us first so we can resolve it quickly. Unresolved chargebacks may result in loss of access
      to the product.
